text: Love the Pork Fillet Set $12.90.  Nice.  Restaurant Quality.  Nice brown Sauce and potent yellow wasabi

Loved it. Good choice of Japanese food around the area. katsu was crispy and I loved the salad with the sauce. I would love to try their curry next time.

Take away charge is 50 cents extra. It came with miso soup as well, hence, 50 cents for 2 containers.

Tried the new menu priced at $10.80, it taste good and food was serve quite fast. Just that I don't find the price worth it especially dining in a non-aircon coffeeshop.

This coffeeshop have a smoking corner and it is warm, so in my own personal opinion pricing can adjust lower.

Love the curry rice. I tried the chicken karaage curry rice and I was very satisfied. Also ordered the black pig don to try and the pork had much fat, but it is quite good. Definitely will return to try other food.

Super duper solid and got standard! Do come here and give it a try if you are craving for legit tonkatsu!!

Crispy on the outside, tender on the inside. Love this so much!! Sauce is great. Personal preference, love eating it with the mustard giving a kick. 5 stars!!
